  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dead of Night: Supermarket is a first-person short indie horror adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras/8295f49c7ae977e0eb2570bb641a5f5c.avif?t=1773515111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras_big/8295f49c7ae977e0eb2570bb641a5f5c.avif?t=1773515111 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Storyline:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a young student stuck with the night shift at a supermarket—a job you despise but is your only option. As you slog through endless, eerie nights, you encounter not only odd customers and deceitful scammers, but also a more sinister presence lurking within the aisles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras/067f22b4c043c9b5ae8b13509da3f64d.avif?t=1773515111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras_big/067f22b4c043c9b5ae8b13509da3f64d.avif?t=1773515111 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playtime:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between 0.5-1 hour, depending on your playstyle.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dead of Night: Supermarket is a first-person short indie horror adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras/8295f49c7ae977e0eb2570bb641a5f5c.avif?t=1773515111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras_big/8295f49c7ae977e0eb2570bb641a5f5c.avif?t=1773515111 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Storyline:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a young student stuck with the night shift at a supermarket—a job you despise but is your only option. As you slog through endless, eerie nights, you encounter not only odd customers and deceitful scammers, but also a more sinister presence lurking within the aisles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras/067f22b4c043c9b5ae8b13509da3f64d.avif?t=1773515111\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441190/extras_big/067f22b4c043c9b5ae8b13509da3f64d.avif?t=1773515111 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playtime:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between 0.5-1 hour, depending on your playstyle.</p>",
